    <entry>
      <title>【队伍安排】</title>
      <link href="/undefined/11/06/hdwindow/"/>
      <url>/undefined/11/06/hdwindow/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="简单滑动窗口-队伍安排"><a href="#简单滑动窗口-队伍安排" class="headerlink" title="[简单滑动窗口][队伍安排]"></a>[简单滑动窗口][队伍安排]</h1><h3 id="题目"><a href="#题目" class="headerlink" title="题目"></a>题目</h3><p><strong>给员工安排队伍，每个队伍固定只能k个人，所有人用数列代表，例如 [1,3,8,7,4,5] 数字被称为能力值<br>要求:<br>1）队伍的人的能力值差异不能超过阈值maxNumber<br>2）每个队伍必须是k个人<br>3）一个人只能在一个队伍中<br>结果：<br>最多能组成多少个队伍？并且返回数据。</strong>  </p><h4 id="示例"><a href="#示例" class="headerlink" title="示例"></a>示例</h4><figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ruby">Test1<br><span class="hljs-meta">&gt;&gt;</span> Array[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">3</span>,<span class="hljs-number">8</span>,<span class="hljs-number">7</span>,<span class="hljs-number">4</span>,<span class="hljs-number">5</span>],k=<span class="hljs-number">3</span>,maxNumber=<span class="hljs-number">3</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">&gt;&gt;</span> [<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">3</span>,<span class="hljs-number">4</span>],[<span class="hljs-number">5</span>,<span class="hljs-number">7</span>,<span class="hljs-number">8</span>],numTeam=<span class="hljs-number">2</span><br><br>Test2<br><span class="hljs-meta">&gt;&gt;</span> Array[<span class="hljs-number">9</span>,<span class="hljs-number">3</span>,<span class="hljs-number">7</span>,<span class="hljs-number">5</span>,<span class="hljs-number">8</span>,<span class="hljs-number">3</span>],k=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,maxNumber=<span class="hljs-number">2</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">&gt;&gt;</span> [<span class="hljs-number">3</span>,<span class="hljs-number">3</span>],[<span class="hljs-number">5</span>,<span class="hljs-number">7</span>],[<span class="hljs-number">8</span>,<span class="hljs-number">9</span>].numTeam=<span class="hljs-number">3</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="题解"><a href="#题解" class="headerlink" title="题解"></a>题解</h4><blockquote><p>题目要求每个队伍的人不能重复，所以这道题就可以用简单的窗口滑动实现，窗口滑动算法可以用来解决一些查找满足一定条件的连续区间的性质(长度等)的问题,考虑到题目要求低，这里就用最简单的方法实现。<br/><br>一、根据题意可知，k为队伍长度，那么最终输出的数组长度应该是k，所以数组中，<code>right-left=k-1</code>。<br/><br>二、为了保证在循环中数组不会越界，就要保证<code>left&lt;=arrays.length-k</code>.<br/><br>三、根据题意每个人只能在一个队伍，不能重复出现，所以如果一旦有数组满足条件，就会跳转到以right+1为开头，长度为k的数组位置上进行判断。<br /></p></blockquote><p><strong>由此可以写出代码</strong></p><figure class="highlight excel"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs excel">public static void moveWindow(<span class="hljs-built_in">int</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">n</span>[],<span class="hljs-built_in">int</span> k,<span class="hljs-built_in">int</span> maxNumber)&#123;<br>    Arrays.sort(<span class="hljs-built_in">n</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span> numTeam=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    while(<span class="hljs-built_in">left</span> &lt;= n.length-k)&#123; <br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>=<span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>+k-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        boolean flag = <span class="hljs-built_in">false</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">if</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">n</span>[<span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>]-<span class="hljs-built_in">n</span>[<span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>]&lt;=maxNumber)&#123;<br>            System.out.println(Arrays.toString(Arrays.copyOfRange(<span class="hljs-built_in">n</span>, <span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>, <span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>))); <br>            flag = <span class="hljs-built_in">true</span>;<br>            numTeam++;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">if</span>(flag)&#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>=<span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        &#125;else&#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>+=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>    System.out.println(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;numTeam = &quot;</span>+numTeam);<br>&#125; <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="图解"><a href="#图解" class="headerlink" title="图解"></a>图解</h4><p>例如，输入的数组Arrays[1，3，9，7，4，5，10，12]，先要把数组进行排序，再进行简单的窗口移动。<br><img src="1.png"></p><hr><blockquote><p>排序好后，进入while循环。<br/><br>left = 0<br/><br>right = 2<br/><br>flag = false<br/><br>numTeam = 0<br/><br><img src="no1.png"><br>arrays[right]-arrays[left] = 3<br/><br>返回 [1，3，4]<br/><br>flag = true<br/><br>numTeam = 1<br/></p></blockquote><hr><blockquote><p>left = left + k = 0+3 = 3<br /><br>right = left + 2 = 3+2 = 5<br/><br><img src="no2.png"><br>arrays[right]-arrays[left] = 4<br/><br>∵ 4 &gt; k<br>flag = false<br/><br>numTeam = 1<br/></p></blockquote><hr><blockquote><p>left = left + 1 = 3+1 = 4<br /><br>right = left + 2 = 4+2 = 6<br/><br><img src="no3.png"><br>arrays[right]-arrays[left] = 3<br/><br>返回 [7,9,10]<br/><br>flag = true<br/><br>numTeam = 2<br/></p></blockquote><hr><blockquote><p>left = left + k = 4+3 = 7<br/><br>∵ 7 &gt; arrays.length-k<br><img src="no4.png"><br>退出while循环<br>输出并结束</p></blockquote><hr><p><br/><br/><br><strong>滑动窗口算法可以解决很多问题，例如最小覆盖子串，字符串排列，找所有字母异位的词等等，今天讲的只是一个最基础的滑动窗口的逻辑，后续文章会继续更新相关题目。</strong></p><hr><h6 id="2021-11-6"><a href="#2021-11-6" class="headerlink" title="2021.11.6"></a>2021.11.6</h6><p>如果您有好的建议或发现了问题，请联系我<a href="mailto:&#x32;&#55;&#49;&#53;&#50;&#48;&#x31;&#x36;&#52;&#x32;&#64;&#x71;&#x71;&#46;&#99;&#111;&#x6d;">&#x32;&#55;&#49;&#53;&#50;&#48;&#x31;&#x36;&#52;&#x32;&#64;&#x71;&#x71;&#46;&#99;&#111;&#x6d;</a><br /><br>欢迎访问<a href="https://uhawblog25.cn/">我的主页</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
