      <title>【基础算法-跳台阶】</title>
      <link href="/undefined/11/04/stepjp/"/>
      <url>/undefined/11/04/stepjp/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="基础算法-跳台阶"><a href="#基础算法-跳台阶" class="headerlink" title="[基础算法-跳台阶]"></a>[基础算法-跳台阶]</h1><h3 id="题目"><a href="#题目" class="headerlink" title="题目"></a>题目</h3><p><strong>一青蛙一次可以跳上1级台阶，也可以跳上2级。</strong><br><strong>问该青蛙跳上一个 n 级的台阶总共有多少种跳法(先后次序不同算不同的结果)？</strong></p><h3 id="题解"><a href="#题解" class="headerlink" title="题解"></a>题解</h3><p><strong>用具体的例子进行推算几种简单的情况，尝试寻找规律</strong><br /></p><blockquote><p>第0个台阶时，无需跳跃，故f(0)=0;<br /></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>第1个台阶时，仅需跳跃1次，故f(1)=1;<br/></p></blockquote><blockquote><p>第2个台阶时，有两种方法：<br/></p><blockquote><p>第一种：每次跳1阶，需要跳2次。<br/><br>第二种：每次跳2阶，需要跳1次。<br/><br>有两种方法，故f(2)=2;<br/></p></blockquote></blockquote><blockquote><p>第3个台阶时，有两个情况：<br/></p><blockquote><p>第一种：第一次跳1阶，那么剩下的2个台阶就相当于跳一次二阶台阶，方法数为f(2);<br/><br>第二种：第一次跳2阶，那么剩下的1个台阶就相当于跳一次一阶台阶，方法数为f(1);<br/><br>故跳三个台阶的方法数f(3)=f(2)+f(1)=3;<br/></p></blockquote></blockquote><p>以此类推，f(4)=f(3)+f(2);<br>根据<code>f(0)=0;f(1)=1;f(2)=2;f(3)=f(2)+f(1)=3;f(4)=f(3)+f(2)=5...</code><br/><br>这就很像我们之前做过的斐波那契数列。于是根据简单的推算可以找到规律<strong>f(n)=f(n-1)+f(n-2);</strong><br/><br/><br><strong>还可以利用逆向思维推理</strong></p><blockquote><p>如果从第n个台阶向下走，那么一次可以走1阶到n-1,或走2阶到n-2,故下楼梯的方法f(n)就等于从n-1走下去的方法加上从n-2走下去的方法，故<strong>f(n)=f(n-1)+f(n-2);</strong></p></blockquote><p>已知<strong>f(0)=0,f(1)=1,f(2)=2,</strong><br>由此可以写出代码：<br/><br/><br><strong>【利用递归】</strong></p><figure class="highlight aspectj"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs aspectj"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">stepJump</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> n)</span></span>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(n==<span class="hljs-number">0</span>)&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-title">if</span><span class="hljs-params">(n==<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)</span></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>&#125;<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-title">if</span><span class="hljs-params">(n==<span class="hljs-number">2</span>)</span></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br>&#125;<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-title">if</span><span class="hljs-params">(n&gt;<span class="hljs-number">0</span>)</span></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> stepJump(n<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>)+stepJump(n<span class="hljs-number">-2</span>);<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>【利用迭代】</strong></p><figure class="highlight arduino"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs arduino"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">stepJump</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> n)</span></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(n==<span class="hljs-number">1</span>||n==<span class="hljs-number">2</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> n;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> stepNum=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> stepOne=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> stepTwo=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">3</span>;i&lt;=n;i++)&#123;<br>        stepNum = stepOne+stepTwo;<br>        stepTwo = stepOne;<br>        stepOne = stepNum;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> stepNum;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当然可以不用递归和迭代，可以选择数组，这个在之前的文章里已经写过了，<a href="http://uhawblog25.cn/undefined/09/21/hawleynew/">点这里查看斐波那契数列数组实现</a>。</p><hr><h6 id="2021-11-4"><a href="#2021-11-4" class="headerlink" title="2021.11.4"></a>2021.11.4</h6><p>如果您有好的建议或发现了问题，请联系我<a href="mailto:&#x32;&#x37;&#x31;&#x35;&#50;&#48;&#49;&#54;&#x34;&#50;&#x40;&#113;&#113;&#46;&#x63;&#111;&#x6d;">&#x32;&#x37;&#x31;&#x35;&#50;&#48;&#49;&#54;&#x34;&#50;&#x40;&#113;&#113;&#46;&#x63;&#111;&#x6d;</a><br /><br>欢迎访问<a href="https://uhawblog25.cn/">我的主页</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
