    <entry>
      <title>【一段有趣的Java代码】</title>
      <link href="/undefined/10/01/isetjava/"/>
      <url>/undefined/10/01/isetjava/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="一段有趣的Java"><a href="#一段有趣的Java" class="headerlink" title="[一段有趣的Java]"></a>[一段有趣的Java]</h1><h3 id="题目"><a href="#题目" class="headerlink" title="题目"></a>题目</h3><p><strong>发现了一段很有意思的java代码，本以为是很简单的输出，结果发现并没有那么简单。<br/><br>下面是代码，猜猜最后的运行结果是什么？</strong></p><figure class="highlight arduino"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs arduino"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">Test</span> &#123;</span><br>  <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">String</span>[] args)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        System.out.<span class="hljs-built_in">println</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;love &quot;</span> + <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">Test</span>());<br>        Test a = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">Test</span>();<br>        a.i++;<br>        System.out.<span class="hljs-built_in">println</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;me &quot;</span> + a.i);<br>    &#125;<br>    <br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">String</span> <span class="hljs-title">toString</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>&#123;<br>        System.out.<span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;I &quot;</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;java &quot;</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="答案"><a href="#答案" class="headerlink" title="答案"></a>答案</h3><figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ruby"><span class="hljs-meta">&gt;&gt;</span>  I love java<br><span class="hljs-meta">&gt;&gt;</span>  me <span class="hljs-number">2</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="题解"><a href="#题解" class="headerlink" title="题解"></a>题解</h3><h3 id="逐步分析"><a href="#逐步分析" class="headerlink" title="逐步分析"></a>逐步分析</h3><p><strong>分析代码首先要做的是了解代码结构并且将复杂的代码分块分析。</strong>在上述代码中，只有一个<code>Test</code>类，但发现除了主函数外还有一个函数<code>public String toString()</code>,所以我们将两个函数分开分析。<br /><br /></p><h4 id="第一步：仅保留主函数运行查看结果"><a href="#第一步：仅保留主函数运行查看结果" class="headerlink" title="第一步：仅保留主函数运行查看结果."></a>第一步：仅保留主函数运行查看结果.</h4><figure class="highlight arduino"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs arduino"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">Test</span> &#123;</span><br>  <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">String</span>[] args)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        System.out.<span class="hljs-built_in">println</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;love &quot;</span> + <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">Test</span>());<br>        Test a = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">Test</span>();<br>        a.i++;<br>        System.out.<span class="hljs-built_in">println</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;me &quot;</span> + a.i);<br>    &#125;<br>  &#125;<br><br>  运行结果<br>  &gt;&gt;  love pack1.Test@<span class="hljs-number">123</span>a439b<br>  &gt;&gt;  me <span class="hljs-number">2</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可见，没有了下面的函数，对第一行的结果是有影响的。但是对<code>me 2</code>这个结果没有影响，因为他是类变量i自加产生的结果，这个就不多说了。<br /><br />那么为什么第一行变成了<code>love pack1.Test@123a439b</code>？<br />逐步看代码</p><figure class="highlight reasonml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs reasonml"><span class="hljs-module-access"><span class="hljs-module"><span class="hljs-identifier">System</span>.</span></span>out.println(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;love &quot;</span> + <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-constructor">Test()</span>);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这一步的结果应该是输出love加上new Test(),这里的new Test()是一个Test类中新的对象。输出应该是什么呢？</p><p><code>System.out.println()</code> 这个方法会<strong>调用传入的所有实参的toString方法</strong>.<br />当我们打印一个对象的引用时，实际是默认调用这个对象的toString()方法.<br />当打印的对象所在类没有重写Object中的toString()方法时，默认调用的是Object类中toString()方法.<br />而通过查询API可以发现toString()的返回值.</p><p><img src="newtest.png"> </p><p><br /><em><strong>getClass().getName() + ‘@’ + Integer.toHexString(hashCode())</strong></em><br /><br>由此我们就可以知道为什么第一行输出结果变成了<code>love pack1.Test@123a439b</code>.</p><h4 id="第二步：了解toString-重写"><a href="#第二步：了解toString-重写" class="headerlink" title="第二步：了解toString()重写"></a>第二步：了解toString()重写</h4><p><strong>重写toString() 只会对类生效，并不能字符串生效</strong><br /><br>例如:</p><figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs typescript"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">pratise</span> </span>&#123;<br>  <br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span> cStr=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;Change&quot;</span>;<br>    <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span> <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">toString</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>)</span>&#123;<br>          <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> cStr ;<br>    &#125;<br>      <br>     <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">static</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">void</span> <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">main</span>(<span class="hljs-params"><span class="hljs-built_in">String</span>[] args</span>)</span>&#123;<br>         <span class="hljs-built_in">String</span> nStr=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;NoChange&quot;</span>;<br>         System.out.println(nStr.toString()); <br>   &#125;<br>&#125;<br><br>运行结果<br>&gt;&gt;  NoChange<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p>上面解释了toString()的输出规则，题目代码中既然有了toString()的重写，那我们就看看题目中的重写是什么.</p><figure class="highlight arduino"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs arduino"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">String</span> <span class="hljs-title">toString</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>&#123;<br>    System.out.<span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;I &quot;</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;java &quot;</span>;<br>&#125;<br><br>该重写中，需要输出<span class="hljs-string">&quot;I &quot;</span>,再返回<span class="hljs-string">&quot;java &quot;</span>.<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>所以在运行<code>System.out.println(&quot;love &quot; + new Test());</code>时，运行之前先解析了new Test()，输出了”I “，解析结束后返回了”java “，所以最后输出结果是”I love java”.<br><br/><br>综上，最后结果为</p><figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs apache"><span class="hljs-attribute">I</span> love java<br><span class="hljs-attribute">me</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h6 id="2021-10-1"><a href="#2021-10-1" class="headerlink" title="2021.10.1"></a>2021.10.1</h6><p>如果您有好的建议或发现了问题，请联系我<a href="mailto:&#50;&#x37;&#x31;&#53;&#x32;&#48;&#49;&#x36;&#x34;&#50;&#64;&#113;&#x71;&#46;&#x63;&#111;&#109;">&#50;&#x37;&#x31;&#53;&#x32;&#48;&#49;&#x36;&#x34;&#50;&#64;&#113;&#x71;&#46;&#x63;&#111;&#109;</a><br /><br>欢迎访问<a href="https://uhawblog25.cn/">我的主页</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
