      <title>【字符串回文】</title>
      <link href="/undefined/09/22/index/"/>
      <url>/undefined/09/22/index/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="每日一题-判断回文"><a href="#每日一题-判断回文" class="headerlink" title="[每日一题][判断回文]"></a>[每日一题][判断回文]</h1><h3 id="题目"><a href="#题目" class="headerlink" title="题目"></a>题目</h3><p><strong>现有一个字符串，请你判断该字符串是否是回文。如果是返回True，否则返回False</strong>  </p><h4 id="示例"><a href="#示例" class="headerlink" title="示例"></a>示例</h4><figure class="highlight smalltalk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs smalltalk">输入：<span class="hljs-comment">&quot;abcba&quot;</span><br>返回：<span class="hljs-keyword">true</span><br><br>输入：<span class="hljs-comment">&quot;qwe&quot;</span><br>返回：<span class="hljs-keyword">false</span><br><br>输入：<span class="hljs-comment">&quot;a&quot;</span><br>返回：<span class="hljs-keyword">true</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="题解"><a href="#题解" class="headerlink" title="题解"></a>题解</h4><h5 id="方法1-【双指针】"><a href="#方法1-【双指针】" class="headerlink" title="方法1 【双指针】"></a><em><strong>方法1 【双指针】</strong></em></h5><p>既然需要判断字符串是否为回文，最简单的办法应该是用字符串的第一个字符和最后一个字符比较，第二个字符和倒数第二个比较……<br>于是可以写出代码：</p><figure class="highlight processing"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs processing"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">boolean</span> judge (<span class="hljs-keyword">String</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>) &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span> len=<span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>.length();<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span> j=len<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;j;i++,j--)&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>.charAt(i)!=<span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>.charAt(j))&#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">false</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">true</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>代码解释</strong></em><br/><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;利用i和j，在for循环中来判断字符串首尾是否相同，如果有一处不同，则不符合题意，返回false，如果全部相同，结束for循环，返回true。<br>举个例子，输入的字符串为”abcba”</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs math">charAt(0)=&#x27;a&#x27;,charAt(1)=&#x27;b&#x27;,charAt(2)=&#x27;c&#x27;,charAt(3)=&#x27;b&#x27;,charAt(4)=&#x27;a&#x27;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>代码开始运行：</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">①第一次：<span class="hljs-attribute">i</span>=0,j=str.length()-1=4; charAt(0)=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>,charAt(4)=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>,正确,继续运行。<br>②第二次：<span class="hljs-attribute">i</span>=1,j=4-1=3; charAt(1)=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;b&#x27;</span>,charAt(3)=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;b&#x27;</span>,正确,继续运行。<br>③第三次：<span class="hljs-attribute">i</span>=2,j=3-1=2; charAt(2)=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;c&#x27;</span>,charAt(2)=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;c&#x27;</span>,正确,继续运行。<br>④第四次：<span class="hljs-attribute">i</span>=3,j=2-1=1; i&gt;j,不符合<span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>循环进入条件,推出循环，执行 return <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;<br><br>返回值为<span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h5 id="方法2-【利用StringBuffer产生新对象】"><a href="#方法2-【利用StringBuffer产生新对象】" class="headerlink" title="方法2 【利用StringBuffer产生新对象】"></a><em><strong>方法2 【利用StringBuffer产生新对象】</strong></em></h5><figure class="highlight processing"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs processing"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">boolean</span> judge (<span class="hljs-keyword">String</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>) &#123;<br>        StringBuffer s1 = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> StringBuffer(<span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>);    <br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>.equals(s1.<span class="hljs-built_in">reverse</span>().toString());<br>    &#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>代码解释</strong></em><br/><br><code>StringBuffer s1 = new StringBuffer();</code>可以初始化一个新的空对象;<br /><br>而代码中<code>StringBuffer s1 = new StringBuffer(str);</code>则是将str中字符串内容赋予s1;<br>这样,s1中的内容就变成了str中的内容.<br />s1经过revers()反转后,要将他转换成String类型,故还要用到toString(),方便进行比较.</p><hr><p><em><strong>[点1]为什么用StringBuffer而不用String呢？</strong></em><br /><br>SringBuffer类和String一样，也用来代表字符串.<br /><br>但是相比String, StringBuffer在进行字符串处理时,不生成新的对象,在内存使用上要优于String类.<br />当遇到插入、删除等字符串操作时,可以考虑用StringBuffer.<br /><br /><br><em><strong>[点2]关于reverse()</strong></em><br /><br>使用<code>reverse()</code>时需要用到 <code>import java.util.*;</code><br /><br><code>reverse()</code>的作用是<strong>反转</strong>，例如字符反转和列表反转.<br /></p><figure class="highlight dart"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dart"><span class="hljs-built_in">StringBuffer</span> s1 = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">StringBuffer</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;abc&quot;</span>);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> s1.reverse();<br> <br>--最终返回值为<span class="hljs-string">&quot;cba&quot;</span>.<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><br /><em><strong>[点3]为什么用equals而不是”==”？</strong></em><br /><br>equals比较的是两个字符串内容是否相等;<br /><br>==比较的是两个字符串的内存地址是否相同。<br /><br>在上述代码中,我们新建了一个新对象StringBuffer s1,明显内存地址是不同的,所以要用到equals();</p><hr><h6 id="2021-9-22"><a href="#2021-9-22" class="headerlink" title="2021.9.22"></a>2021.9.22</h6><p>如果您有好的建议或发现了问题，请联系我<a href="mailto:&#x32;&#x37;&#49;&#53;&#50;&#48;&#x31;&#54;&#x34;&#50;&#64;&#113;&#113;&#46;&#99;&#x6f;&#109;">&#x32;&#x37;&#49;&#53;&#50;&#48;&#x31;&#54;&#x34;&#50;&#64;&#113;&#113;&#46;&#99;&#x6f;&#109;</a><br /><br>欢迎访问<a href="https://uhawblog25.cn/">我的主页</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
