        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="每日一题-斐波那契数列"><a href="#每日一题-斐波那契数列" class="headerlink" title="[每日一题][斐波那契数列]"></a>[每日一题][斐波那契数列]</h1><h3 id="题目"><a href="#题目" class="headerlink" title="题目"></a>题目</h3><p><strong>现要求输入一正整数n，请你输出斐波那契数列的第n项。(n&lt;30)</strong><br>斐波那契数列要满足以下条件：  </p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs math">fib(x) = 1(x=1,2) <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs math">fib(x) = fib(x-1)+fib(x-2)(x&gt;2)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="示例"><a href="#示例" class="headerlink" title="示例"></a>示例</h4><figure class="highlight gcode"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs gcode">输入：<span class="hljs-number">4</span><br>返回值：<span class="hljs-number">3</span><br>解释：fib<span class="hljs-comment">(1)</span>=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,fib<span class="hljs-comment">(2)</span>=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,fib<span class="hljs-comment">(3)</span>=fib<span class="hljs-comment">(3-1)</span>+fib<span class="hljs-comment">(3-2)</span>=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,fib<span class="hljs-comment">(4)</span>=fib<span class="hljs-comment">(4-1)</span>+fib<span class="hljs-comment">(4-2)</span>=<span class="hljs-number">3</span>  <br>故返回值为<span class="hljs-number">3</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h4 id="题解"><a href="#题解" class="headerlink" title="题解"></a>题解</h4><h4 id="方法1-【递归法】"><a href="#方法1-【递归法】" class="headerlink" title="方法1 【递归法】"></a><em><strong>方法1 【递归法】</strong></em></h4><p>根据斐波那契数列性质可知，从第三位起，每一位的计算方法都为<code>fib(n)=fib(n-1)+fib(n-2)</code><br>那就可以用if对n的值进行判断，根据公式直接写出代码：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">Solution</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">Fibonacci</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> n)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(n&lt;=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>)&#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>&#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> Fibonacci(n-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)+Fibonacci(n-<span class="hljs-number">2</span>);<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>代码解释</strong></em><br/></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs math">Fibonacci:1,1,2,3,5,8,13,21……<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>因为斐波那契数列前两位都是1，所以当n&lt;2时，返回值都为1.<br /><br>当n&gt;2时，则需要用到公式<code>Fibonacci(n)=Fibonacci(n-1)+Fibonacci(n-2)</code><br /><br>当n&gt;2时就返回这个值。</p><h6 id="递归法解释"><a href="#递归法解释" class="headerlink" title="递归法解释"></a><em><strong>递归法解释</strong></em></h6><p>递归法的核心就是<strong>调用自身</strong><br /><br>举一个例子，在上述代码中，如果输入的值为3，则需要进入<code>else</code>运行。</p><figure class="highlight reasonml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs reasonml">输入n=<span class="hljs-number">3</span>;<br>因为n&gt;<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,故return <span class="hljs-constructor">Fibonacci(3-1)</span>+<span class="hljs-constructor">Fibonacci(3-2)</span><br><span class="hljs-constructor">Fibonacci(3-1)</span>又会调用我们写的<span class="hljs-constructor">Fibonacci(<span class="hljs-params">int</span> <span class="hljs-params">n</span>)</span>函数，因为此时n=<span class="hljs-number">3</span>-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>，故返回值为<span class="hljs-number">1</span>；<br><span class="hljs-constructor">Fibonacci(3-2)</span>也会调用<span class="hljs-constructor">Fibonacci(<span class="hljs-params">int</span> <span class="hljs-params">n</span>)</span>函数，此时n=<span class="hljs-number">3</span>-<span class="hljs-number">2</span>=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>，故返回值为<span class="hljs-number">1</span>；<br><br>综合上述过程，<span class="hljs-constructor">Fibonacci(3)</span>=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h4 id="方法2-【调用数组】"><a href="#方法2-【调用数组】" class="headerlink" title="方法2 【调用数组】"></a><em><strong>方法2 【调用数组】</strong></em></h4><p>假设我们需要第5位的斐波那契数，则就利用for循环给array数组赋值，一直赋值到array[4]为止(数组从0开始)，输出array[4]的值。<br /></p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title">Solution</span> &#123;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">Fibonacci</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> n)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> array[] = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span>[<span class="hljs-number">40</span>];<br>        array[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        array[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>;i&lt;n;i++)&#123;<br>            array[i] = array[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>] + array[i<span class="hljs-number">-2</span>];<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> array[n<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>];<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><em><strong>代码解释</strong></em><br/></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs math">array[0]=1,array[1]=1,array[2]=2,array[3]=3,array[4]=5……<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">输入4时；<br>则<span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>循环会变成：<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-attribute">i</span>=2;i&lt;4;i++)&#123;<br>    array[i] = array[i-1] + array[i-2];<br>&#125;<br>①第一次循环：<span class="hljs-attribute">i</span>=2,array[2]=array[1]+array[0]=1+<span class="hljs-attribute">1</span>=2;<br>②第二次循环：<span class="hljs-attribute">i</span>=3,array[3]=array[2]+array[1]=2+<span class="hljs-attribute">1</span>=3;<br>③第三次循环：<span class="hljs-attribute">i</span>=4，不符合i&lt;4，退出循环。<br>④返回array[4-1]=array[3]=3;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h5 id="2021-9-21"><a href="#2021-9-21" class="headerlink" title="2021.9.21"></a>2021.9.21</h5><p>如果您有好的建议或发现了问题，请联系我<a href="mailto:&#x32;&#x37;&#x31;&#53;&#50;&#48;&#49;&#x36;&#52;&#50;&#x40;&#113;&#113;&#x2e;&#x63;&#111;&#109;">&#x32;&#x37;&#x31;&#53;&#50;&#48;&#49;&#x36;&#52;&#50;&#x40;&#113;&#113;&#x2e;&#x63;&#111;&#109;</a><br /><br>欢迎访问<a href="https://uhawblog25.cn/">我的主页</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
